data.description: This sweet 2/2 charmer (possible 3 bedrooms!) sits in the heart of beautiful Drain. Conveniently & centrally located, only minutes from shopping and schools with short commute times; approx 40 minutes to Eugene and Roseburg. This home boasts of a newer; roof, flooring, carpets, trim, and sewer line, as well as a big backyard with storage and possible RV parking. With 2 large bedrooms, with one that has a conjoining bonus room that could act as an office or a 3rd bedroom, this home really could have it all!  This sweet home is just waiting for your personal touches. All appliances are included. Don't wait!  Come see it today.
